<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Response to Your Support Request: {{ticketId}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { background-color: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin: 10px 0; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; }
        .response { 
            background-color: #f8fafc; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
        }
        .ticket-info { 
            background-color: #f9fafb; 
            padding: 12px; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #9ca3af;
        }
        .agent-signature {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Response to Your Support Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for contacting GoUraan Support. Here's the latest update on your ticket:</p>
        
        <div class="ticket-info">
            <p><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> {{ticketId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Subject:</strong> {{subject}}</p>
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{status}}</p>
            <p><strong>Priority:</strong> {{priority}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="response">
            <p><strong>Response from {{agentName}}:</strong></p>
            <p>{{{message}}}</p>
            
            {{#if attachments}}
            <p><strong>Attachments:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                {{#each attachments}}
                <li><a href="{{this.url}}" target="_blank">{{this.name}}</a> ({{this.size}})</li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="agent-signature">
                <p>Best regards,<br>
                {{agentName}}<br>
                {{agentTitle}}<br>
                GoUraan Support Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can view the complete conversation and respond to this message by clicking the button below:</p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{ticketUrl}}" class="button">View Full Conversation</a>
        </p>
        
        <p>If you have any additional information to share, please reply directly to this email or click the button above to respond through our support portal.</p>
        
        <p>We appreciate your patience and thank you for choosing GoUraan!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
        <p>© {{currentYear}} GoUraan. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
